Subject: Re: [T2] Re: [VB] Wheel bolt torque

On my 74 bus, I torque the wheel lug nuts to 75 ft-lb. I use my beam
type torque wrench because 75 is to high for a standard clicker. I
have a line drawn in permanent marker on the dial of the beam wrench
at 75 so I can see.

Scott B
